Skills	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Internal	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Relying on strength and endurance, laborers earn a living through hard, physical work. This category includes soldiers and others who use weapons for a living.	KEY:Laborer ~ Skills																		CSKILL:Climb|Jump|Swim									SOURCEPAGE:DD
