#	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.YuanTiCultistClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:On reaching 10th level, a yuan-ti cultist attains the pinnacle of his career, transcending his mortal essence to become an emissary of Merrshaulk. His type changes to outsider, but he can be raised from the dead if willing. He gains spell resistance equal to 20 + his Wisdom Modifier. In addition, the Voice of Merrshaulk gains the supernatural ability to communicate telepathically with any other creature within 100 feet that has a language. He can also command other yuan-ti at will, as Dominate Monster cast as a divine spell by a cleric of the cultist's class level (including cleric levels). This is a spell-like, mind-affecting compulsion effect.	KEY:Yuan-Ti Cultist ~ Voice of Merrshaulk																		TEMPLATE:Voice of Merrshaulk								SORTKEY:Class_Yuan-Ti_Cultist	SOURCEPAGE:SS
